{"tid":1631865,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"知唔知點解要出禁蒙面法","createTime":"2019-10-06T16:27:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T17:44:15.000Z","uid":150315,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"46195d3dc2958353a3ccc2337ab849e3cd6f41b3","tid":1631865,"uid":150315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:27:01.000Z","msg":"對面就想我地升級到國際認可既暴動<br />\n等美國無借口拎香港做彈藥制裁支那<br />\n順便拎正牌實彈清場<br />\n想趕係十月底前以快打慢<br />\n<br />\n示威者根本唔需要急於求勝<br />\n呢場仗係可以打夠十年<br />\n弱者呢個身份先係我地保護罩<br />\n創意令我地得到本地同國際既認可<br />\n<br />\n如果有一日有哂同級武器資源<br />\n不妨升級到對等武力<br />\n<br />\n我地要既係用抗爭拖到佢倒台/回應訴求<br />\n唔係用武力擊破政府<br />\n對面仲有錢有槍<br />\n武力從來唔係我地唯一戰場<br />\n經濟戰先係港人最強手段<br />\n<br />\n認清目標同手段<br />\n最重要就係唔割<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0873da917d8ed66f8daa671767b4b257355e5db1","tid":1631865,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:27:15.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n【重開】［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630849\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630849</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"57210ec107c73b8281aac2cdf03c11ccc4179fac","tid":1631865,"uid":150315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:28:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1ac19b9185d55dbda151427a1966051680b45068","tid":1631865,"uid":249794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:28:27.000Z","msg":"你知我知大家都知<br />\n諗下係咩人可以遊行完返到屋企前就洗版<br />\n凌晨大家訓教又帶風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9747b4d2b2b4b84ae682bda573b0c331ea7fa2a0","tid":1631865,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:28:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對店舖:記住唔需要次次硬裝修</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話、EMAIL、無限FAX</span></span></strong><br />\n想同職員談心又得，講咩都得，幫阿SIR叫下外賣又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知JAM到佢線就得。有EMAIL既就SEND EMAIL查詢下，有FAX機既可以用下無限FAX大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2.MEMO紙</span></span></strong><br />\n有開門就入去叫杯水慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3.善用1823</span></span></strong><br />\n食完野集體食物中毒呀，消防設備唔合符規格呢D無理由唔投訴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留意返打完1823之後，佢係要起限期內比返回覆你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢招長玩長有，大家打之前要謹慎少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">4.蟲系魔法師</span></span></strong><br />\n知道好多巴絲打鐘意養蟲蟲，但係入店一定要小心唔好倒瀉D寶貝呀(特別起食肆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對人(限影大頭相/沒有攻擊性/非主攻類):</span></strong></span><br />\n記住召喚神獸唔係唔得，必須記住係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">對家首先用武力/拎住武器先可以召喚</span></strong></span><br />\n但係對住非攻擊形對手都召喚既話觀感就唔係太好睇，仲比左機會對家有煲大<br />\n對住非攻擊形既我地可以幫佢<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">飛個靚髮</span></span></strong>或者<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">化下妝</span></span></strong>就夠，唔一定要下下爆哂缸先叫成功架<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">*要記住中年人著緊自己把頭髮仲多過條命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejjnAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejjnAS</a>"},{"pid":"7931ee2875ef5c2d0b48b7178247af6101c68aed","tid":1631865,"uid":301929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:29:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vW2nV3L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvW2nV3L.png&h=6943bd03&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"81de33f64aa4c43b34097294ea8dc208d244f7f9","tid":1631865,"uid":150315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7931ee2875ef5c2d0b48b7178247af6101c68aed","tid":1631865,"uid":301929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:29:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vW2nV3L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvW2nV3L.png&h=6943bd03&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:29:48.000Z","msg":"好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26148d40cfb2a968706e52023cfc12f2eb72ef92","tid":1631865,"uid":171259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:29:50.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bc7046b915ca09ef8304aec1b72cd37b2bb6110","tid":1631865,"uid":78947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:30:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58f6c77f43f206cd2011d243cd79047f53e96f4f","tid":1631865,"uid":150315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:44:15.000Z","msg":"push"}]}